.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, house, metal, punk, reggae, salsa, trance
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, chess, woodworking, dancing, skydiving, baking, magic-tricks
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is between the fan of reggae and the fan of metal##2
 3. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 4. the fan of trance is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the fan of d&b is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the writer is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
14. the fan of house is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
