 5. the photographer is the person who likes emerald##1
 6. the videographer is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the left of the bartender##1
12. the person who likes blue is between the dancer and the person who likes ebony##2
13. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
